- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with improving policy transfer by matching behavior in simulation and the real world.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve vision-based perception in the real-world tasks.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with adapting simulation parameters to improve policy transfer.
